description:
YOU ARE A FUCKING ARTIST - Art by Saami Heyes

This NFT comes with a physical token, which can be redeemed after up until 2 months of purchase. 

If the physical token is not redeemed, it is destroyed after 2 months.

Size available: 
12” x 12” inches
24" x 24" inches

Printed on archival giclee paper

Shipping times may vary.

Shipping fees will be calculated and due at the time of shipping 

The buyer must contact Saami Heyes to redeem the physical token and arrange for shipping. 
The physical token is optional
